.com%2Fgoogle-openai-anthropic-ai-agents-training-data-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20Overview%20sure%20thinks%20it's%20real%2C%20and%20will%20happily%20give%20you%20a%20detailed%20answer%20of%20what%20the%20phrase%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fembed.bsky.app%2Fstatic%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-bluesky-cid%3D%5C%22bafyreigfsnvalkyrj5wuxtuwkaoqewzhsdzbd6tmnm24y3ncgsod3rmaya%5C%22%20data-bluesky-embed-color-mode%3D%5C%22system%5C%22%20data-bluesky-uri%3D%5C%22at%3A%2F%2Fdid%3Aplc%3Aknlwbyvg36keh64h6awokbqx%2Fapp.bsky.feed.post%2F3lnhxkdywzc2m%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESomeone%20on%20Threads%20noticed%20you%20can%20type%20any%20random%20sentence%20into%20Google%2C%20then%20add%20%E2%80%9Cmeaning%E2%80%9D%20afterwards%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20get%20an%20AI%20explanation%20of%20a%20famous%20idiom%20or%20phrase%20you%20just%20made%20up.%20Here%20is%20mine%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsky.app%2Fprofile%2Fdid%3Aplc%3Aknlwbyvg36keh64h6awokbqx%2Fpost%2F3lnhxkdywzc2m%3Fref_src%3Dembed%5C%22%3E%5Bimage%20or%20embed%5D%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Greg%20Jenner%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsky.app%2Fprofile%2Fdid%3Aplc%3Aknlwbyvg36keh64h6awokbqx%3Fref_src%3Dembed%5C%22%3E%40gregjenner.bsky.social%3C%2Fa%3E)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsky.app%2Fprofile%2Fdid%3Aplc%3Aknlwbyvg36keh64h6awokbqx%2Fpost%2F3lnhxkdywzc2m%3Fref_src%3Dembed%5C%22%3EApril%2023%2C%202025%20at%206%3A15%20AM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Jenner%2C%20a%20British%20historian%20and%20podcaster%2C%20saw%20people%20talking%20about%20this%20phenomenon%20on%20Threads%20and%20wanted%20to%20try%20it%20himself%20with%20a%20made-up%20idiom.%20The%20badger%20phrase%20%26quot%3Bjust%20popped%20into%20my%20head%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20I