20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680a8fd4c6ad288d147f1338%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22433%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BThe%20road%20is%20full%20of%20salsa.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBasically%2C%20AI%20Overviews%20aren't%20perfect%20(duh)%2C%20and%20these%20fake%20idioms%20are%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20premise%26quot%3B%20searches%20that%20are%20purposely%20intended%20to%20trip%20it%20up%20(fair%20enough).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20does%20try%20to%20limit%20the%20AI%20Overviews%20from%20answering%20things%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bdata%20voids%2C%26quot%3B%20i.e.%2C%20when%20there%20are%20no%20good%20web%20results%20to%20a%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20clearly%2C%20it%20doesn't%20always%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20some%20ideas%20about%20what's%20going%20on%20here%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20it%20is%20good%20and%20useful%2C%20some%20of%20it%20isn't.%20As%20one%20might%20even%20say%2C%20it's%20a%20%3Cem%3Emixed%20bag%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20first%2C%20one%20more%20made-up%20phrase%20that%20Google%20tried%20hard%20to%20find%20meaning%20for%3A%20%26quot%3BDon't%20kiss%20the%20doorknob.%26quot%3B%20Says%20Google's%20AI%20Overview%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22don't%20kiss%20the%20doorknob%20google%20search%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680a9065c6ad288d147f1361%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22407%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20kiss%20the%20doorknob.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what's%20going%20on%20here%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Good%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnglish%20is%20full%20of%20idioms%20like%20%26quot%3Bkick%20the%20bucket%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bpiece%20of%20cake.%26quot%3B%20These%20can%20be%20confusing%20if%20English%20isn't%20your%20first%20language%20(and%20frankly%2C%20they're%20often%20confusing%20for%20native%20speakers%2C%20too).%20My%20case%20in%20point%20is%20that%20the%20phrase%20is%20commonly%20misstated%20as%20%26quot%3Bcase%20and%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20makes%20lots%20of%20sense%20that%20people%20would%20often%20be%20Googling%20to%20understand%20the%20meaning%20of%20a%20phrase%20they%20came%20across%20that%20they%20don't%20understand.%20And%20in%20theory%2C%20this%20is%20a%20great%20use%20for%20the%20AI%20Overview%20answers%3A%20You%20want%20to%20see%20the%20simply-stated%20answer%20right%20away%2C%20not%20click%20on%20a%20link.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Bad%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20%3Cem%3Eshould%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20really%20good%20at%20this%20particular%20thing.%20LLMs%20are%20trained%20on%20vast%20amounts%20of%20the%20English%20written%20language%20%E2%80%94%20reams%20of%20books%2C%20websites%2C%20YouTube%20transcriptions%2C%20etc.%2C%20so%20being%20able%20to%20recognize%20idioms%20is%20something%20they%20should%20be%20very%20good%20at%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20it's%20making%20mistakes%20here%20is%20not%20ideal.%20What's%20going%20wrong%20that%20Google's%20AI%20Overview%20isn't%20giving%20the%20real%20answer%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3BThat%20isn't%20a%20phrase%2C%20you%20idiot%26quot%3B%3F%20Is%20it%20just%20a%20classic%20AI%20hallucination%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20ugly%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComparatively%2C%20ChatGPT%20gave%20a%20better%20answer%20when%20I%20asked%20it%20about%20the%20badger%20phrase.%20It%20told%20me%20that%20it%20was%20not%20a%20standard%20English%20idiom%2C%20even%20though%20it%20had%20the%20vaguely%20folksy%20sound%20of%20one.%20Then%20it%20offered%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20%3Cem%3Etreat%20it%20like%20a%20real%20idiom%3C%2Fem%3E%20(for%20fun)%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20gave%20a%20possible%20definition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20this%20isn't%20a%20problem%20across%20%3Cem%3Eall%3C%2Fem%3E%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20Google%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22badger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F54ad097edd0895f84c8b463d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222591%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can't%20lick%20a%20badger%20twice%3F%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FRussell%20Cheyne%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20somewhat%20different%20from%20last%20year's%20Google%20AI%20Overview%20answers%20fiasco%20where%20the%20results%20pulled%20in%20information%20from%20places%20like%20Reddit%20without%20considering%20sarcasm%20%E2%80%94%20remember%20when%20it%20suggested%20people%20should%20eat%20rocks%20for%20minerals%20or%20put%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-glue-pizza-i-tried-it-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglue%20in%20their%20pizza%3C%2Fa%3E%20(someone%20on%20Reddit%20had%20once%20joked%20about%20glue%20in%20pizza%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20be%20where%20it%20drew%20from).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20all%20very%20low-stakes%20and%20silly%20fun%2C%20making%20up%20fake%20phrases%2C%20but%20it%20speaks%20to%20the%20bigger%2C%20uglier%20problems%20with%20AI%20becoming%20more%20and%20more%20enmeshed%20in%20how%20we%20use%20the%20internet.%20It%20means%20Google%20searches%20are%20somehow%20worse%2C%20and%20since%20people%20start%20to%20rely%20on%20these%20more%20and%20more%2C%20that%20bad%20information%20is%20just%20getting%20out%20there%20into%20the%20world%20and%20taken%20as%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20AI%20search%20will%20get%20better%20and%20more%20accurate%2C%20but%20what%20growing%20pains%20will%20we%20endure%20while%20we're%20in%20this%20middle%20phase%20of%20a%20kinda%20wonky%2C%20kinda%20garbage-y%2C%20slop-filled%20AI%20internet%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20here%2C%20it's%20already%20changing%20our%20lives.%20There's%20no%20going%20back%2C%20the%20horse%20has%20left%20the%20barn.%20Or%20as%20they%20sa