%20in%20my%20mind%2C%20traveling%20was%20a%20justifiable%20need%20%E2%80%94%20something%20I%20had%20to%20do%20to%20satisfy%20my%20soul.%20I%20was%20living%20life%20to%20the%20fullest%20and%20living%20it%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20anticipation%20leading%20up%20to%20a%20trip%20and%20the%20excitement%20I%20felt%20during%20the%20trip%20or%20vacation%20were%20what%20I%20lived%20for.%20To%20me%2C%20traveling%20is%20the%20ultimate%20definition%20of%20fun%2C%20and%20I%20had%20loads%20of%20it%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20always%20came%20to%20a%20screeching%20halt%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20stepped%20off%20the%20plane%20and%20back%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20really%20good%20at%20ignoring%20the%20stress%20of%20adulting%20and%20paying%20bills.%20And%20not%20only%20did%20I%20get%20good%20at%20ignoring%20my%20obligations%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20but%20I%20became%20a%20rock%20star%20at%20spending%20every%20last%20dime%20of%20my%20paycheck%20like%20it%20would%20be%20my%20last%2C%20which%20didn't%20allow%20me%20to%20plan%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20things.%20That%20only%20added%20to%20my%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20realized%20that%20getting%20rid%20of%20my%20debt%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20%2457%2C000%20when%20including%20%2448%2C000%20in%20student%20loans%20%E2%80%94%20would%20mean%20less%20stress%20and%20more%20of%20an%20ability%20to%20live%20life%20to%20the%20fullest%2C%20my%20idea%20of%20living%20well%20shifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222691420d-51d2-42ac-a548-3ac1ed46c0dc%5C%22%3EI%20used%203%20strategies%20to%20pay%20off%20%2457%2C000%20in%20debt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20days%20of%20Googling%20and%20piecing%20together%20a%20lot%20of%20personal-finance%20research%20and%20advice%2C%20I%20crafted%20a%20plan%20to%20help%20me%20get%20out%20of%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac4ba799-a86e-4eb2-beb4-73cc60080cd0%5C%22%3E1.%20I%20found%20a%20budgeting%20system%20that%20worked%20for%20me%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of