m-solving%20and%20communication%20skills%2C%20applicable%20in%20multiple%20fields.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20story%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Mike%20Crabtree%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20Data%20Engineering%20at%20Ford.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20I%20had%20just%20received%20my%20associate's%20degree%20in%20industrial%20mechanics%20and%20electronics%20engineering.%20Then%2C%20the%20recession%20flooded%20the%20labor%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20crowded%20field%2C%20my%20degree%20and%20resume%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20retail%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20didn't%20stand%20out%20as%20much%20to%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20pursued%20a%20bachelor's%20in%20business%20and%20computer%20information%20systems%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20needed%20to%20differentiate%20myself%20more.%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fleadership-management-coursera-edx-linkedin-learning-online-courses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaking%20paid%20online%20courses%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20platforms%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fcoursera-pricing-and-best-courses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoursera%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fedx-overview-faq%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EedX%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fwhat-is-udacity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUdacity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20earning%20certifications%20in%20everything%20from%20business%20analytics%20to%20leadership%20skills%20that%20I%20shared%20on%20my%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20didn't%20major%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fdata-science-courses-online%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20science%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20took%20supplemental%20online%20classes%20that%20helped%20me%20stand%20out%20and%20pivot%20into%20the%20field.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-gm-sales-increases-before-auto-tariffs-donald-trump-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFord%3C%2Fa%3E%20reached%20out%20months%20after%20I%20graduated%20in%202016.%20The%20company%20hired%20me%20as%20a%20data%20scientist%20that%20November%2C%20a%20role%20I%20stayed%20in%20for%20five%20years%20before%20becoming%20the%20manager%20of%20a%20data%20engineering%20team.%20After%20leaving%20Ford%20to%20work%20for%20a%20data-specific%20organization%2C%20I%20returned%20in%202023%20and%20eventually%20became%20the%20director%20of%20data%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20the%20job%20market%20is%20a%20little%20tougher%20to%20break%20into%2C%20let%20alone%20stay%20in.%20Some%20people%20are%20looking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarketers-are-trying-to-make-themselves-recession-proof-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecession-proof%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20jobs%20amid%20concerns%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-jobs-impact-disruption-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20disruption%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecession-2025-outlook-economy-downturn-trump-tariffs-china-small-business-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomic%20uncertainty%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20experience%20taught%20me%20that%20the%20key%20is%20to%20keep%20learning.%20By%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Echoosing%20challenging%20online%20courses%2C%20I%20tapped%20into%20skills%20I%20never%20used%20before%2C%20from%20technical%20ones%20like%20programming%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoft-skills-leaders-need-for-success-2016-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoft%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20helped%20me%20grow%20as%20a%20manager.%20Taking%20classes%20in%20everything%20from%20entrepreneurship%20to%20self-driving%20car%20engineering%20also%20signaled%20to%20managers%20that%20I%20was%20proactive%20and%20willing%20to%20learn%20%E2%80%94%20qualities%20that%20are%20important%20for%20feeling%20secure%20at%20a%20job%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-promoted-faster-dice-president-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20a%20promotion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20three%20ways%20to%20recession-proof%20your%20job%20as%20much%20as%20you%20can%20%E2%80%94%20or%20land%20a%20more%20stable%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4c19a8f-0058-4d3e-9434-2f4b71468879%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFind%20your%20gaps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20feel%20like%20you're%20in%20good%20standing%20at%20your%20job%20or%20that%20you're%20prepared%20for%20upcoming%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einterviews%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20as%20well-rounded%20as%20possible.%20If%20you're%20incredibly%20self-aware%2C%20you%20might%20already%20know%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkplace-trends-for-2025-shrm-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskill%20gaps%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Personally%2C%20I%20didn't%20learn%20mine%20until%20I%20started%20challenging%20myself%20with%20online%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20statistics%20and%20the%20scientific%20method%20are%20foundational%20in%20data%20science%2C%20I%20took%20a%20statistics%20course.%20I%20got%20stumped%20on%20probability%20and%20had%20to%20improve%20my%20understanding%20before%20I%20could%20move%20forward.%20Later%2C%20I%20took%20a%20machine%20learning%20class%20and%20realized%20that%20linear%20algebra%20wasn't%20my%20strong%20suit.%20In%20addition%20to%20learning%20the%20needed%20technical%20skills%20from%20those%20courses%2C%20I%20also%20learned%20how%20to%20spot%20my%20weaknesses%20%E2%80%94%20and%20take%20action%20to%20fix%20them%20by%20studying%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20apply%20to%20all%20fields.%20You%20might%20be%20a%20manager%2C%20for%20example%2C%20and%20need%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleadership-training-signs-you-need-it-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleadership%20training%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20your%20job%20doesn't%20directly%20offer%20many%20opportunities%20to%20push%20yourself%20outside%20your%20comfort%20zone%2C%20courses%20can%20help%20you%20quickly%20spot%20what%20you%20struggle%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7be4d05-bbbb-452e-ba02-b1a131bcb42e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrow%20your%20problem-solving%20skills%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20able%20to%20think%20critically%2C%20solve%20problems%2C%20and%20lean%20into%20your%20intuition%20makes%20you%20a%20more%20valued%20team%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20news%20is%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20stuff%20your%20brain%20with%20as%20many%20facts%20or%20programming%20techniques%20as%20you%20think.%20It's%20more%20important%20to%20be%20able%20to%20assess%20direction%2C%20build%20business%20acumen%2C%20and%20make%20confident%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20know%20how%20to%20build%20a%20linear%20model%20as%20well%20as%20AI%20does.%20But%20when%20you%20can%20just%20look%20that%20up%2C%20what%20matters%20more%20is%20realizing%20that%20a%20linear%20model%20isn't%20the%20best%20solution%20to%20a%20problem%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20I%20beefed%20up%20my%20critical%20thinking%20skills%20was%20by%20taking%20a%20course%20in%20quantum%20computing%20taught%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fibm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIBM%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20heavily%20involved%20physics%20%E2%80%94%20something%20I%20wasn't%20an%20expert%20in%20at%20all.%20It%20taught%20me%20to%20think%20quickly%20and%20wrap%20my%20head%20around%20a%20lot%20of%20conceptu