vorite%20material%20for%20woks%20because%20it%20reacts%20quickly%20to%20heat%20adjustments%20and%20has%20a%20natural%20nonstick%20surface%20once%20seasoned.%20But%20be%20warned%3A%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20heavy%2C%20repeated%20usage%20to%20get%20to%20this%20level%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it's%20not%20recommended%20for%20the%20casual%20home%20cook%2C%20and%20why%20we%20did%20not%20include%20any%20carbon%20steel%20woks%20in%20this%20test.%20We%20are%20looking%20forward%20to%20testing%20some%20pre-seasoned%20carbon%20steel%20woks%20for%20the%20next%20update%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECast%20iron%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20bit%20more%20accessible%20as%20people%20are%20more%20accustomed%20to%20maintaining%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20important%20to%20bear%20in%20mind%20that%20it's%20a%20very%20heavy%20material%20and%20will%20limit%20your%20maneuverability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStainless%20steel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20has%20been%20growing%20in%20Western%20popularity%20since%20it's%20durable%20and%20not%20prone%20to%20rust.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAluminum%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20woks%20are%20lighter%20and%20hotter%20but%20prone%20to%20warp%20and%20ding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHard%20anodized%20and%20nonstick%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20pans%20provide%20greater%20ease%20of%20use%20in%20a%20familiar%20medium%2C%20but%20their%20performance%20will%20vary%20based%20on%20manufacturer-determined%20specs%2C%20like%20thickness%20and%20finish.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHandles%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20There%20are%20two%20main%20types%20of%20handles%20on%20the%20best%20woks%3A%20loop%20and%20stick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20loop-handled%2C%20or%20Canton%20wok%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20meant%20for%20tumble%20cooking%2C%20which%20means%20using%20a%20scoop%20and%20spatula%20to%20quickly%20agitate%20ingredients%20(like%20fried%20rice)%20and%20spark%20faster%20liquid%20evaporation%20and%20spot%20charring.%20Loop-handled%20woks%20are%20also%20great%20for%20pan-frying%2C%20which%20requires%20constant%20contact%20with%20the%20heat%20source%3B%20steaming%3B%20and%20big%20batch%20cooking%2C%20as%20they%20traditionally%20tend%20to%20be%20wider%20than%20long-handled%20woks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong-handled%20or%20stick-handled%20woks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20are%20meant%20for%20toss%20cooking%2C%20such%20as%20with%20saucy%20dishes%20and%20stir-fries%20that%20incorporate%20larger-cut%20ingredients.%20In%20this%20technique%2C%20you%20lift%20the%20wok%20off%20the%20burner%20and%20toss%20the%20ingredients%20into%20the%20air%20using%20a%20shake%20of%20your%20wrist.%20Traditional%20long-handled%20woks%20offer%20a%20deeper%20basin%20in%20the%20middle%20for%20thickening%20sauces%20and%20higher%20walls%2C%20and%20are%20lightweight%20for%20maneuverability%20in%20order%20to%20flip%20and%20toss%20off%20the%20burner.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228de9956f-08b3-446a-8b7a-21d3fb71974c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%20woks%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20woks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fried%20rice%20sits%20inside%20a%20wok%20as%20part%20of%20testing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60bfb2c42feb6f00181ed9ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20all%20of%20our%20wok%20tests%2C%20we%20used%20the%20same%20high-powered%20burner%20of%20a%20gas%20stove.%3Cp%3ESu-Jit%20Lin%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%2016%20of%20the%20best%20woks%20of%20various%20materials%2C%20looking%20at%20construction%20quality%20and%20scratch%20resistance%3B%20heat%20retention%20and%20distribution%3B%20ease%20of%20cleaning%20and%20handling%3B%20and%20overall%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20each%20wok%2C%20I%20made%20two%20dishes%20chosen%20for%20the%20multiple%20Asian%20cooking%20techniques%20they%20required%2C%20and%20utilized%20high%20smoke-point%2C%20neutral%20avocado%20oil%20to%20provide%20a%20cleaner%20background%20for%20any%20sign%20of%3Cem%3E%20wok%20hei%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%A6%20should%20it%20be%20achieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewoksoflife.com%2Fchinese-chicken-broccoli-brown-sauce%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChinese%20takeout-style%20chicken%20with%20broccoli%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20in%20a%20brown%20sauce%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshowed%20us%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHow%20effectively%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewoksoflife.com%2Fhow-to-velvet-chicken-stir-fry%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evelveted%20chicken%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20achieve%20browning%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHow%20tender%20the%20chicken%20would%20remain%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20dry%20vegetables%20could%20achieve%20wok%20hei-like%20char%20in%20this%20pan%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20bulky%20vegetables%20could%20resist%20steaming%20in%20a%20crowded%20pan%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAny%20hot%20spots%20or%20inconsistencies%20in%20heat%20dispersion%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHow%20fast%20and%20evenly%20sauces%20would%20reduce%20and%20thicken%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHow%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20coat%20ingredients%20in%20the%20sauce%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEase%20of%20handling%20and%20cleanup%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20to%20use%20the%20same%20heat%20setting%20for%20each%20wok%2C%20but%20differing%20heat%20retention%20levels%20forced%20adaptation%20to%20avoid%20ruining%20the%20dish.%20I%20also%20used%20more%20oil%20for%20stainless%20steel%20woks%20to%20avoid%20sticking%2C%20and%20added%20broth%20to%20the%20fried%20rice%20in%20some%20instances%20since%20some%20materials%20were%20more%20apt%20to%20burn%20than%20char%20and%20required%20more%20moisture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESteak%20summer%20fried%20rice%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einspired%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%2