3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EM%C3%93G%C5%AA%20Modern%20Chinese%20Kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%20founder%20Mike%20Wang%2C%20developer%20of%20his%20restaurant's%20self-cooking%20robo-woks%20with%20his%20GenX%20Robotics%20division%2C%20puts%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Bhas%20everything%20to%20do%20with%20the%20mathematics%20of%20particle%20movement.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20science%20of%20woking%20is%20broken%20down%20to%20temperature%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explains%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20is%20done%20by%20elevating%20the%20wok%20with%20the%20hand%2C%20controlling%20the%20gas%20lever%20with%20one's%20leg%20during%20cooking%2C%20and%20flipping%20the%20ingredients%20inside%20the%20wok.%20At%20GenX%20Robotics%20and%20M%C3%93G%C5%AA%2C%20we%20studied%20the%20science%20of%20woking%20by%20using%20computer%20vision%20to%20track%20the%20movements%20of%20individual%20particles%20and%20how%20they%20move%20with%20the%20different%20viscosities%20of%20sauce.%20We%20investigated%20how%20those%20ingredients%20interacted%20with%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20cooking%20pan%2C%20the%20sauce%2C%20and%20other%20food%20particles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20he%20and%20his%20team%20found%20was%20that%20the%20slightest%20variation%20could%20lead%20to%20notably%20different%20outcomes%2C%20which%20our%20own%20testing%20confirms%20on%20a%20broader%20scale.%20The%20takeaway%3A%20be%20patient%20as%20you%20learn%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20your%20wok.%20A%20learning%20curve%20is%20to%20be%20expected%20at%20first%2C%20but%20you'll%20soon%20be%20able%20to%20produce%20consistent%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e319d8c6-8047-4218-9169-4f776c01b6bf%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Pro%20tip%3A%20temper%20your%20expectations%5C%22%3EPro%20tip%3A%20temper%20your%20expectations%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20what%20wok%20you%20get%2C%20though%2C%20just%20know%20that%20results%20on%20an%20electric%20stove%20will%20be%20considerably%20less%20favorable%20than%20on%20a%20gas%20stove.%20And%20that%20same%20gas%20stove%20will%20fall%20well%20shy%20of%20what%20a%20commercial%20restaurant%20wok%20burner%20can%20produce.%20If%20you're%20looking%20to%20recreate%20a%20dish%20you%20had%20at%20a%20restaurant%2C%20be%20prepared%20for%20at%20least%20slightly%20different%20results%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20working%20on%20an%20electric%20stove.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20home%20stove%20will%20be%20as%20immediately%20responsive%2C%20either.%20The%20instantaneousness%20of%20being%20able%20to%20crank%20up%20the%20heat%20and%20adjust%20it%20fast%20is%20a%20huge%20part%20of%20wok%20cooking.%20While%20certain%20materials%20help%20with%20heat%20distribution%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20consider%20the%20thickness%2C%20flexibility%2C%20flat%20surface%20area%2C%20and%20curvature%20of%20the%20wok%2C%20too.%20All%20of%20these%20contribute%20to%20its%20quality%20and%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20get%20started%20cooking%20with%20the%20best%20wok%2C%20it'll%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20until%20you%20master%20it%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20with%20that%2C%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20your%20wok%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStart%20with%20a%20great%20wok%20(like%20one%20of%20our%20picks)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUse%20a%20gas%20stove%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUse%20the%20most%20powerful%20burner%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETurn%20up%20the%20heat%20so%20the%20flames%20come%20up%20the%20side%20of%20the%20wok%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EControl%20temperature%20by%20lifting%20the%20wok%20off%20the%20burner%20and%20moving%20items%20that%20are%20cooking%20too%20fast%20to%20the%20walls%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22622d3929-848b-4bc2-bd87-a9ee7264a445%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Wok%20FAQs%5C%22%3EWok%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chicken%20and%20broccoli%20prepared%20in%20a%20wok%20as%20part%20of%20testing.%5C%22%20