%20Fields%20and%20took%20them%20home%20to%20taste-test%20with%20my%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20we'd%20rank%20them%20from%20worst%20to%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223000bf57-a916-4038-a08a-f6931d529c27%5C%22%3EThe%20cookie%20from%20Mrs.%20Fields%20was%20our%20least%20favorite%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22818%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chocolate%20chip%20cookie%20on%20a%20white%20plate%20with%20a%20Mrs.%20Fields%20bag%20behind%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6802a159a466d2b74ab39d0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mrs.%20Fields%20cookie%20wasn't%20bad%2C%20but%20I%20preferred%20the%20others%20more.%20%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMrs.%20Fields%20is%20the%20most%20established%20of%20the%20cookie%20brands%20we%20sampled.%20The%20company%20was%20founded%20in%20Palo%20Alto%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-united-kingdom-to-los-angeles-differences-surprising-things-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalifornia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%201977%20by%20Debbi%20Fields.%20Today%2C%20the%20company%20has%20250%20locations%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cookie%20from%20Mrs.%20Fields%20was%20the%20smallest%20of%20the%20three%20I%20tried%20but%20also%20the%20least%20expensive%20(%242).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerfectly%20round%20and%20evenly%20cooked%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20looked%20like%20a%20slightly%20larger%20version%20of%20a%20chewy%20Chips%20Ahoy%20cookie.%20Nothing%20was%20unappetizing%20about%20its%20appearance%2C%20but%20it%20was%20easily%20the%20least%20exciting%20of%20the%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20took%20a%20bite%2C%20I%20noticed%20it%20had%20a%20bit%20of%20crunch%20around%20the%20outside.%20Nothing%20about%20the%20flavor%20was%20unpleasant%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20sweet%2C%20probably%20the%20least%20salty%20of%20the%20three%20cookies%2C%20and%20soft%20on%20the%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20found%20the%20inside%20was%20soft%20and%20a%20bit%20gummy%2C%20which%20I%20didn't%20love.%20It%20also%20had%20the%20smallest%20portion%20of%20chocolate%20chips%20of%20the%20three%20we%20tried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20were%20careful%20to%20note%20that%20they%20loved%20all%20three%20cookies%2C%20but%20we%20all%20ranked%20this%20one%20as%20our%20least%20favorite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e2b47d38-0565-4f7b-94e2-9e2013429e63%5C%22%3EThe%20Crumbl%20cookie%20was%20good%2C%20but%20I%20prefer%20the%20brand's%20other%20flavors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22961%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chocolate%20chip%20cookie%20on%20a%20white%20plate%2C%20with%20a%20pink%20Crumbl%20box%20behind%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6802a144a466d2b74ab39d02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22721%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cookie%20from%20Crumbl%20was%20huge.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20three%20cookie%20brands%20I%20stopped%20at%2C%20Crumbl%20is%20the%20newest.%20Founded%20in%20Logan%2C%20Utah%2C%20in%202017%2C%20the%20chain%20now%20has%20over%201%2C000%20locations%20across%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-family-to-puerto-rico-for-job-hated-it-left-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuerto%20Rico%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20experience%20with%20Crumbl%20cookies%2C%20so%20I%20knew%20what%20to%20expect%3A%20an%20enormous%2C%20soft%20cookie%20served%20warm%20and%20loaded%20with%20thick%20chunks%20of%20chocolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20semi-sweet%20chocolate%20chunk%20cookie%20cost%20%245%2C%20but%20it%20was%20big%20enough%20for%20several%20people%20to%20share.%20Most%20of%20Crumbl's%20offerings%20are%20visually%20compelling%2C%20and%20this%20one%20certainly%20would've%20made%20for%20the%20best%20Instagram%20post