%22%3EAgrivoltaics%3A%20transforming%20farmers%20into%20entrepreneurs%20with%20agency%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReasoning%20why%20farmers%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20view%20agrivoltaics%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Crisky%20affair%E2%80%9D%2C%20Vivek%20Saraf%2C%20founder%20of%20SunSeed%20APV%2C%20part%20of%20the%20team%20that%20launched%20the%20Parbhani%20project%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20risk%20is%20all%20ours.%20Farmers%20are%20stakeholders%20in%20agrivoltaic%20projects.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20get%20a%20better%20income%20than%20they%20did%20earlier%2C%20but%20without%20the%20risk.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20down%20the%20nuances%20of%20the%20model%2C%20Vivek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20farmer%20typically%20growing%20a%20staple%20crop%20earns%20a%20maximum%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20per%20acre%20per%20year.%20In%20agrivoltaics%2C%20he%20can%20earn%20Rs%2050%2C000%20just%20as%20the%20lease%20for%20the%20land.%20So%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20asking%20him%20to%20sell%20the%20land.%20He%20can%20even%20choose%20to%20work%20on%20this%20farm%20and%20earn%20money.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351525%2Ffarming-profitable-how-to-make-natural-pesticides-himachal-couple-zero-budget-natural-earns-double%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efarmer%20has%20doubled%20his%20income%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fagrivoltaics-8-1745326879.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farmers%20can%20earn%20more%20by%20leasing%20out%20their%20land%20to%20organisations%20interested%20in%20venturing%20into%20agrivoltaics%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vivek%20Saraf%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fagrivoltaics-8-1745326879.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fagrivoltaics-8-1745326879-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fagrivoltaics-8-1745326879-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fagrivoltaics-8-1745326879-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fagrivoltaics-8-1745326879-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-422262%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFarmers%20can%20earn%20more%20by%20leasing%20out%20their%20land%20to%20organisations%20interested%20in%20venturing%20into%20agrivoltaics.%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vivek%20Saraf%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVimal%20Panjwani%20of%20AgriVijay%20concedes.%20Farmers%20mustn%E2%80%99t%20be%20anxious%2C%20he%20weighs%20in.%20One%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20marketplaces%20of%20renewable%20energy%20products%20for%20farmers%20and%20rural%20households%2C%20AgriVijay%E2%80%99s%20success%20lies%20in%20having%20irrigated%20500%20acres%20of%20land%20through%20solar.%20Vimal%20points%20out%20how%20the%20model%20could%20be%20a%20buffer%20for%20financial%20distress%20that%20many%20farmers%20otherwise%20find%20themselves%20grappling%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20find%20it%20tough%20to%20believe%20in%20the%20advantages%20of%20agrivoltaics%2C%20because%20it%20is%20something%20they%20cannot%20see%20yet%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vimal%20weighs%20in.%20%E2%80%9CUnderstandably%2C%20individual%20farmers%20will%20always%20be%20anxious%20about%20installing%20these%20projects%20on%20their%20farms%2C%20but%20when%20a%20group%20of%20farmers%20comes%20together%20as%20an%20organisation%20and%20installs%20a%20solar%20farm%2C%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20reduce%20their%20electricity%20expenses.%E2%80%9D%20Only%20once%20farmers%20see%20the%20benefits%20in%20real%20time%20will%20it%20elicit%20a%20tacit%20acceptance%20of%20the%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVimal%20illustrates%20how%20farmers%20can%20capitalise%20on%20this%3A%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20say%20farmers%20are%20currently%20buying%20electricity%20at%20Rs%208%20or%209%20per%20unit.%20Once%20they%20install%20agrivoltaics%2C%20electricity%20will%20be%20sold%20to%20them%20for%20Rs%205%2C%20which%20is%20cheaper.%20This%20way%2C%20they%20are%20minimising%20their%20expenditure%20and%20reducing%20their%20dependency%20on%20the%20grid.%E2%80%9D%20For%20farmers%20who%20are%20still%20apprehensive%20about%20the%20model%20going%20against%20the%20grain%2C%20Vimal%20has%20another%20solution.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D314%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Faskagrivijay%252Fvideos%252F404259222478618%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D560%26t%3D0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22314%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgriVijay%20has%20launched%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20%E2%80%98Vertical%20Bifacial%20Solar%20AgriVoltaics%20Project%E2%80%99%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Next2Sun%20and%20Wattkraft%2C%20in%20Maharashtra.%20%E2%80%9COur%20innovative%20Agri-PV%20system%20is%20designed%20to%20simultaneously%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F420549%2Fbhaskar-solar-lantern-in-indian-villages-green-energy-projects-in-rural-indian-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20solar%20energy%20production%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20agriculture%2C%20maintaining%20over%2090%20percent%20land%20usability%20for%20farming.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20approach%20not%20only%20optimises%20land%20use%20but%20also%20ensures%20soil%20preservation%2C%20garnering%20substantial%20public%20support.%20By%20s